---
title: One-Pot Creamy Pumpkin Fusilli with Parmesan & Parsley
description: What’s going into the risoni today? A little bit of leek, a heap of roasted pumpkin and a creamy tomato-based sauce. It’s a perfect concoction of flavour, texture and pure yumminess.

*We’ve replaced the risoni in this recipe with fusilli due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66178e4d300be64307bdf780-267902af.jpeg
